text: Christine Bjerendal (born 3 February 1987) is a Swedish archer. Bjerendal competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics, 2016 Summer Olympics, and 2020 Summer Olympics.Christine BjerendalChristine BJERENDAL == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden
